              <text>Despite <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">subsection (1)</citation></changeable>, if the registration of a foreign restraining order in New Zealand is extended as a result of an application to the High Court, it expires on the date specified by the High Court under <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">section 144</citation></changeable>.</text>
